{"tid":1810335,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警方濫權】明報A1: 被捕精神病者三求服藥 警不理 涉違警察通例","createTime":"2020-01-03T19:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T23:55:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae2071084b5d813ec7aae5a28ba6a1140ea264e3","tid":1810335,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/81859134_2779031468823637_1872180419034611712_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=R8LXj0kTY-wAQkfRmSJ5iD24rWFbPBXAwBKyg9WkmhBrCJK8JJfDbnsvA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=a5b9954d4e6efcc86c05491f8114126e&amp;oe=5EAAFF8C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F81859134_2779031468823637_1872180419034611712_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3DR8LXj0kTY-wAQkfRmSJ5iD24rWFbPBXAwBKyg9WkmhBrCJK8JJfDbnsvA%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Da5b9954d4e6efcc86c05491f8114126e%26oe%3D5EAAFF8C&h=9dd28543&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa1efcd1b55e4139f25c8d3b2bff3a85c52d836a","tid":1810335,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:11:58.000Z","msg":"民陣元旦日遊行被腰斬後，警方在銅鑼灣大圍捕逾400人，多名無辜巿民被拘押。警方被批評濫捕，另又被揭疑對精神上無行為能力者（MIP）濫權。<br />\n有在反修例示威被捕的精神病康復者控訴，拘留期間向3名警員三度要求服藥，警員均置之不理，質疑她「玩嘢」，最終拖延逾24小時才再服藥，保釋後病情惡化，需加重用藥劑量。警方亦涉嫌違反《警察通例》，未有即時安排合適成人或律師陪同事主錄取口供。香港社會工作者總工會會長倫智偉表示，知悉有約13宗MIP或抑鬱病患被捕個案，部分人無法即時與家人或社工會面，有急切醫療需要卻不獲即時處理。立法會議員張超雄批評警方漠視MIP被捕人權益，不將指引放在眼內"},{"pid":"ef2c213be73ff356c2c3910f563f82f718d0dce8","tid":1810335,"uid":221265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:23:41.000Z","msg":"明報雖然奶咗共<br />\n但啲記者成日身體突破到缺口"},{"pid":"8273e6a4899e1992c5c779dbe1cfe04edec82834","tid":1810335,"uid":98386,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T19:35:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾張超雄淨識批評 又唔見有啲實際性既野做下"},{"pid":"8270cc6245f12b36cc6dc47f684ae05a9aeaafbc","tid":1810335,"uid":325346,"like":1,"disli